title: Impacting Future Generations | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Impacting Future Generations | Joel Osteen
description:
God wants you to be free from everything that's trying to limit you. You don't have to live under negative patterns passed down from those who came before you. You can be the one to set a new trend for future generations. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
